{
  "stem": "2522.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, it can be freezing outside, but you can dig yourself into a hayrick and s-- or, or rotting straw is ideal.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I would say that, that Luja was a buddy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He sort of looked at me as, you know, this, this kid, this pitiful kid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I always in this partisan scene, I was seen as the pitiful kid, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What is this 15-year-old kid doing in a place like this?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, everybody was older, older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in other words, the-- for instance, Tatko, the communist from the Spanish Civil War, was in his-- in his late 40s, and most of the people who survived, you know, serious guys, were in their 20 and the 30s.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was really the kid, the kid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And but I, I got the same rations as everybody else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Cigarettes were one of the key elements of ration.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the currency-- liquor and cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I always traded my cigarettes for bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In one of my, my recollections about smoking is that here were people who had very little food, and they knew that if they don't eat, they will really be weak and they'll not be able to march because we continually marched.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yet they're trading bread and lard for cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, well, that's one of the reasons I never want to smoke.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I always traded my cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We did raids on villages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We did raids on villages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We intercepted here and there some trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, we were sort of a band.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I perfectly can understand the Croatians and the Serbs and all of those bands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were a band.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were a 12th-century kind of a band of, of military desperadoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
